---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AppShell from '../components/layout/AppShell.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Digital Wardrobe">
	<AppShell active="/terms">
		<section class="bg-canvas-soft py-16">
			<div class="container-page max-w-3xl">
				<p class="font-mono text-xs text-body mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">Legal & security</p>
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-10 tracking-tight text-ink md:text-5xl md:leading-[56px] mb-8">
					Terms & conditions.
				</h1>
				
				<div class="prose max-w-none text-sm leading-7 text-body space-y-6">
					<p class="text-base text-ink font-medium">
						Last updated: June 17, 2026
					</p>
					
					<p>
						Welcome to Digital Wardrobe. By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Please read them carefully.
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-3">1. Use of the service</h2>
					<p>
						Digital Wardrobe provides outfit planning, visual cataloging, and closet insights. You agree to use the service only for lawful personal purposes. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your session token and access settings.
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-3">2. User content license</h2>
					<p>
						You retain all intellectual property rights and full ownership of any photos, text, or styling data you upload to Digital Wardrobe. By uploading content, you grant us a limited, secure, private license to host and process your assets solely to display them to you and perform the requested analyses (e.g. background removal, cost-per-wear stats).
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-3">3. Acceptable use</h2>
					<p>
						You agree not to upload any content that:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4 space-y-1">
						<li>Infringes on any third-party intellectual property or copyright.</li>
						<li>Is harmful, threatening, abusive, defamatory, or otherwise objectionable.</li>
						<li>Contains software viruses or any code designed to disrupt the service.</li>
					</ul>

					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-3">4. Limitation of liability</h2>
					<p>
						Digital Wardrobe is provided on an "as-is" and "as available" basis. While we strive to maintain high service availability and keep your visual closet secure, we do not guarantee that the service will be entirely error-free or uninterrupted.
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-8 mb-3">5. Modification of terms</h2>
					<p>
						We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted directly to this page with an updated modification date. Your continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of any updated terms.
					</p>

					<p class="mt-8 text-xs text-mute border-t border-hairline pt-6">
						If you have any questions or concerns regarding these Terms & Conditions, please contact us at support@wardrobe-closet.com.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</AppShell>
</Layout>
